% Python Language Ontology - CNL Format
% Extends oo_ontology.cnl with Python-specific concepts
%
% This ontology maps Python-specific concepts to the generic OO ontology.
% All Python entities should use the unified CNL names with language="python".

% ============================================================================
% Python-Specific Entity Types
% ============================================================================

% Core entities
Every python-module is a module.
Every python-class is a class.
Every python-method is a method.
Every python-function is a function.
Every python-parameter is a parameter.

% Python attributes map to fields
Every python-attribute is a field.

% Import types
Every python-import is an import.
Every python-from-import is a python-import.

% Exception handling
Every python-try-block is a try-block.
Every python-except-handler is a catch-clause.
Every python-finally-block is a finally-clause.
Every python-try-else-block is a try-else-block.
Every python-raise-statement is a throw-statement.

% Control flow
Every python-return-statement is a return-statement.
Every python-with-statement is a with-statement.
Every python-context-manager is a context-manager.

% Other
Every python-assignment is an assignment.
Every python-reference is a reference.

% ============================================================================
% Python-Specific Concepts
% ============================================================================

% Decorators
Every decorated-function is a function.
Every decorated-class is a class.
Every decorated-method is a method.

% Special methods
Every dunder-method is a method.
Every magic-method is a dunder-method.
Every python-constructor is a dunder-method.
Every python-destructor is a dunder-method.

% Comprehensions
Every list-comprehension is an expression.
Every dict-comprehension is an expression.
Every set-comprehension is an expression.
Every generator-expression is an expression.

% Async
Every async-function is a function.
Every async-method is a method.
Every coroutine is a function.

% ============================================================================
% Python Exception Handling Patterns
% ============================================================================

% Bare except - catches everything (antipattern)
Every bare-except is a catch-clause.

% General except - catches Exception or BaseException
Every general-except is a catch-clause.

% Silent swallow - catches and ignores (antipattern)
Every silent-swallow-except is a catch-clause.

% ============================================================================
% Python Code Smells
% ============================================================================

% Exception swallowing
Every exception-swallower is a method.

% Missing type hints
Every untyped-function is a function.
Every untyped-parameter is a parameter.

% Long parameter lists
Every function-with-many-params is a function.
